704169f-a.title: Brooklyn: Fenimore Street - Rogers Avenue
704169f-a.text:
298-312 Fenimore Street, south side, east of Rogers Ave. A rear
view of homes on Fenimore Street, on the south line of what was once Leffert's
Farm.
1922.
Eugsne L. Armbruster Collection.
